{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852464470,"sessionID":"ses_286f28ce6ffep8ntWwTGOpmVoB","part":{"id":"prt_d790e229d001BnyYyvncwoVQFi","messageID":"msg_d790e08f60015mog30FGLr0pmd","sessionID":"ses_286f28ce6ffep8ntWwTGOpmVoB","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-c34c30c8d9c24abfae8486a562db6b50","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: | Item | Value |\n5: |------|-------|\n6: | AR | AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 |\n7: | Module | `pkg/router` |\n8: | Language | Go |\n9: | Size | M |\n10: | Stage | ST-1 |\n11: \n12: ## Architecture\n13: ```\n14: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n15: │                      HTTP Request                            │\n16: └─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n17:                       │\n18:                       ▼\n19: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n20: │                  JWT Middleware                              │\n21: │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐         │\n22: │  │   Parser    │──│  Validator  │──│  Extractor  │          │\n23: │  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘         │\n24: └─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n25:                       │\n26:                       ▼\n27: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n28: │                    Handler                                   │\n29: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n30: \n31: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n32: │                    JWT Service                               │\n33: │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐         │\n34: │  │   Signer    │  │  Verifier   │  │  Refresher  │          │\n35: │  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘         │\n36: │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐           │\n37: │  │           Key Manager (HS256/RS256)          │           │\n38: │  └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘           │\n39: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n40: ```\n41: \n42: ## Design\n43: ### Component Relationships\n44: | Component | Role | Dependencies |\n45: |-----------|------|--------------|\n46: | JWTService | Token 签发与验证 | KeyManager, Config |\n47: | AuthMiddleware | HTTP 请求认证 | JWTService |\n48: | KeyManager | 密钥管理 | Config |\n49: | TokenRefresher | Token 刷新 | JWTService |\n50: \n51: ## Data Structures\n52: ```go\n53: // JWTConfig JWT 配置\n54: type JWTConfig struct {\n55:     SecretKey      string        // HS256 密钥\n56:     PrivateKey    string        // RS256 私钥\n57:     PublicKey     string        // RS256 公钥\n58:     Algorithm     string        // HS256 或 RS256\n59:     TokenExpiry   time.Duration // Token 有效期\n60:     RefreshExpiry time.Duration // 刷新 Token 有效期\n61:     Issuer        string        // 签发者\n62: }\n63: \n64: // Claims JWT 声明\n65: type Claims struct {\n66:     UserID   string                 `json:\"user_id\"`\n67:     Roles    []string               `json:\"roles\"`\n68:     Metadata map[string]interface{} `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n69:     jwt.RegisteredClaims\n70: }\n71: \n72: // TokenPair Token 对\n73: type TokenPair struct {\n74:     AccessToken  string `json:\"access_token\"`\n75:     RefreshToken string `json:\"refresh_token\"`\n76:     ExpiresIn    int64  `json:\"expires_in\"`\n77:     TokenType    string `json:\"token_type\"`\n78: }\n79: ```\n80: \n81: ## API Contracts\n82: ### 签发 Token\n83: | Method | Path | Description |\n84: |--------|------|-------------|\n85: | POST | /auth/token | 签发新 Token |\n86: | POST | /auth/refresh | 刷新 Token |\n87: \n88: ### Request/Response\n89: ```go\n90: // TokenRequest 签发请求\n91: type TokenRequest struct {\n92:     UserID   string                 `json:\"user_id\"`\n93:     Roles    []string               `json:\"roles,omitempty\"`\n94:     Metadata map[string]interface{} `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n95: }\n96: \n97: // TokenResponse 签发响应\n98: type TokenResponse struct {\n99:     AccessToken  string `json:\"access_token\"`\n100:     RefreshToken string `json:\"refresh_token\"`\n101:     ExpiresIn    int64  `json:\"expires_in\"`\n102:     TokenType    string `json:\"token_type\"`\n103: }\n104: ```\n105: \n106: ## Error Handling\n107: | Error | Code | Description |\n108: |-------|------|-------------|\n109: | ErrTokenExpired | 401 | Token 已过期 |\n110: | ErrTokenInvalid | 401 | Token 无效 |\n111: | ErrTokenMissing | 401 | Token 缺失 |\n112: | ErrTokenRefreshFailed | 401 | Token 刷新失败 |\n113: \n114: ## Testing Strategy\n115: - 单元测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n116: - 集成测试覆盖主要流程\n117: - 边界测试：过期、篡改、格式错误\n118: - 性能测试：Token 签发 QPS\n119: \n120: ## Validation Checklist\n121: - [ ] JWTService 实现 Sign/Verify/Refresh 方法\n122: - [ ] AuthMiddleware 实现请求拦截\n123: - [ ] 支持 HS256 和 RS256 算法\n124: - [ ] 配置化过期时间\n125: - [ ] 完整错误处理\n126: \n127: ## Open Questions\n128: 1. 是否需要支持 Token 黑名单？\n129: 2. 是否需要支持多租户场景？\n130: 3. 密钥轮换策略？\n131: \n132: ## References\n133: - [golang-jwt/jwt](https://github.com/golang-jwt/jwt)\n134: - [RFC 7519](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519)\n\n(End of file - total 134 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Design\n\n## Overview\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 |\n| Module | `pkg/router` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n## Architecture\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      HTTP Request                            │\n└─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n                      │\n                      ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                  JWT Middleware                              │","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/design.md","time":{"start":1775852464455,"end":1775852464468}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852464472,"sessionID":"ses_286f28ce6ffep8ntWwTGOpmVoB","part":{"id":"prt_d790e25a4001G9ueO3QHqHUhS2","messageID":"msg_d790e08f60015mog30FGLr0pmd","sessionID":"ses_286f28ce6ffep8ntWwTGOpmVoB","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-ed6c2a7b87fb4f518c35ee58eed518fc","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-010/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-010/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-010 — Router 会话管理 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-010 — Router 会话管理 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/router` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: The Router module provides HTTP-based session routing for AgentCube sandboxes. It manages session lifecycle, routes incoming invocation requests to appropriate sandbox pods via reverse proxy, and handles JWT-based authentication for secure communication between Router and Workload Manager.\n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: ## Architecture\n18: \n19: ### System Context\n20: \n21: ```\n22: ┌─────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\n23: │   Client SDK    │────▶│     Router      │────▶│  WorkloadMgr    │\n24: │ (Python/CLI)    │     │  (pkg/router)   │     │(pkg/workloadmgr)│\n25: └─────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘\n26:                               │                         │\n27:                               │                         │\n28:                               ▼                         ▼\n29:                         ┌─────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\n30:                         │   Session Store │     │   Kubernetes    │\n31:                         │ (Redis/Memory)  │     │   API Server    │\n32:                         └─────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘\n33: ```\n34: \n35: ### Request Flow\n36: \n37: ```\n38: Client Request (with x-agentcube-session-id header)\n39:        │\n40:        ▼\n41: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n42: │ 1. Concurrency Limit Middleware (semaphore channel)      │\n43: │    - Reject with 429 if max concurrent exceeded          │\n44: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n45:        │\n46:        ▼\n47: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n48: │ 2. Logging Middleware                                    │\n49: │    - Record request method, path, duration               │\n50: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n51:        │\n52:        ▼\n53: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n54: │ 3. Recovery Middleware                                   │\n55: │    - Panic recovery → 500 response                       │\n56: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n57:        │\n58:        ▼\n59: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n60: │ 4. handleInvoke (AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter)           │\n61: │    - Extract namespace, name, path from URL params       │\n62: │    - Get sessionID from x-agentcube-session-id header    │\n63: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n64:        │\n65:        ▼\n66: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n67: │ 5. SessionManager.GetSandboxBySession                    │\n68: │    - If sessionID empty → create new sandbox             │\n69: │    - If sessionID provided → lookup from store           │\n70: │    - On not found → SessionNotFoundError                 │\n71: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n72:        │\n73:        ▼\n74: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n75: │ 6. UpdateSessionLastActivity (before proxy)              │\n76: │    - Update LastActivity timestamp in store              │\n77: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n78:        │\n79:        ▼\n80: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n81: │ 7. Entry Point Selection                                 │\n82: │    - selectEntryPoint: prefix match or first entry       │\n83: │    - buildTargetURL: construct backend URL               │\n84: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n85:        │\n86:        ▼\n87: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n88: │ 8. JWT Generation (for Sandbox/SandboxClaim kinds)       │\n89: │    - JWTManager.GenerateToken with session claims        │\n90: │    - RS256 signing with RSA 2048-bit key                 │\n91: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n92:        │\n93:        ▼\n94: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n95: │ 9. Reverse Proxy                                         │\n96: │    - httputil.NewSingleHostReverseProxy                  │\n97: │    - Director: rewrite URL, add forwarding headers       │\n98: │    - ModifyResponse: set x-agentcube-session-id          │\n99: │    - ErrorHandler: connection refused → 502, timeout→504│\n100: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n101:        │\n102:        ▼\n103: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n104: │ 10. UpdateSessionLastActivity (after proxy)              │\n105: │    - Update activity timestamp again                     │\n106: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n107: ```\n108: \n109: ---\n110: \n111: ## Design\n112: \n113: ### Component Relationships\n114: \n115: | Component | Role | Dependencies |\n116: |-----------|------|--------------|\n117: | `Server` | Gin HTTP server, route registration, graceful shutdown | `Config`, `SessionManager`, `Store`, `JWTManager`, `Logger` |\n118: | `sessionManager` | Session lookup, sandbox creation via Workload Manager | `Store`, `http.Client` (to WorkloadMgr) |\n119: | `JWTManager` | RS256 JWT token generation, key persistence | `rsa.PrivateKey`, Kubernetes client (optional) |\n120: | `ReverseProxyWrapper` | Request director, response modification, error handling | `url.URL`, JWT string |\n121: | `Store` (interface) | Session/sandbox CRUD, activity tracking | Redis or in-memory implementation |\n122: | `middleware.go` | Concurrency limiting, logging, panic recovery | `gin.Context`, `Logger` |\n123: | `errors.go` | Custom error types with APIStatus interface | None |\n124: \n125: ### Dependencies\n126: \n127: | Package | Purpose | Import Path |\n128: |---------|---------|-------------|\n129: | Gin | HTTP router and middleware | `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` |\n130: | JWT | JWT token generation and signing | `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` |\n131: | HTTP2 | HTTP/2 transport configuration | `golang.org/x/net/http2` |\n132: | Kubernetes API | APIStatus error interface | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors` |\n133: | Klog | Logging | `k8s.io/klog/v2` |\n134: | Common Types | SandboxInfo, CreateSandboxRequest/Response | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types` |\n135: \n136: ---\n137: \n138: ## Data Structures\n139: \n140: ### Config (`config.go`)\n141: \n142: ```go\n143: type Config struct {\n144:     Port                  string  // Default \":8080\"\n145:     EnableTLS             bool    // TLS mode toggle\n146:     TLSCert               string  // TLS certificate file path\n147:     TLSKey                string  // TLS key file path\n148:     MaxConcurrentRequests int     // Semaphore size, default 1000\n149:     Debug                 bool    // Gin debug mode toggle\n150: }\n151: ```\n152: \n153: ### Server (`server.go`)\n154: \n155: ```go\n156: type Server struct {\n157:     config         *Config\n158:     engine         *gin.Engine\n159:     httpServer     *http.Server\n160:     sessionManager SessionManager\n161:     storeClient    Store\n162:     httpTransport  *http.Transport\n163:     jwtManager     *JWTManager\n164:     logger         Logger\n165: }\n166: ```\n167: \n168: ### sessionManager (`session_manager.go`)\n169: \n170: ```go\n171: type sessionManager struct {\n172:     storeClient     Store\n173:     workloadMgrAddr string         // From WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL env\n174:     httpClient      *http.Client   // Timeout: 2m, HTTP/2 enabled\n175: }\n176: ```\n177: \n178: ### JWTManager (`jwt.go`)\n179: \n180: ```go\n181: type JWTManager struct {\n182:     privateKey *rsa.PrivateKey  // 2048-bit RSA key\n183:     publicKey  *rsa.PublicKey\n184: }\n185: \n186: const (\n187:     rsaKeySize         = 2048\n188:     jwtExpiration      = 5 * time.Minute\n189:     IdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"\n190:     PrivateKeyDataKey  = \"private.pem\"\n191:     PublicKeyDataKey   = \"public.pem\"\n192: )\n193: \n194: var IdentityNamespace = \"default\" // Overridden by AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE\n195: ```\n196: \n197: ### SandboxInfo (`pkg/common/types/sandbox.go`)\n198: \n199: ```go\n200: type SandboxInfo struct {\n201:     Kind               string\n202:     SandboxID          string\n203:     SandboxNamespace   string\n204:     SandboxName        string\n205:     Name               string\n206:     SessionID          string\n207:     CreatedAt          time.Time\n208:     ExpiresAt          time.Time\n209:     Status             string\n210:     EntryPoints        []SandboxEntryPoint\n211:     UserToken          string              // Optional\n212:     ServiceAccount     string              // Optional\n213:     ServiceAccountName string              // Optional\n214:     LastActivity       time.Time           // Optional\n215: }\n216: \n217: type SandboxEntryPoint struct {\n218:     Path     string  // URL path prefix\n219:     Protocol string  // \"http\" or \"https\"\n220:     Endpoint string  // Backend host:port or full URL\n221: }\n222: ```\n223: \n224: ### ReverseProxyWrapper (`reverse_proxy.go`)\n225: \n226: ```go\n227: type ReverseProxyWrapper struct {\n228:     director       func(*http.Request)\n229:     modifyResponse func(*http.Response) error\n230:     errorHandler   func(http.ResponseWriter, *http.Request, error)\n231: }\n232: ```\n233: \n234: ### Interfaces (`doc.go`)\n235: \n236: ```go\n237: type Store interface {\n238:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n239:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandbox *types.SandboxInfo) error\n240:     UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n241: }\n242: \n243: type Logger interface {\n244:     Info(msg string, keysAndValues ...any)\n245:     Error(msg string, keysAndValues ...any)\n246:     Warning(msg string, keysAndValues ...any)\n247: }\n248: \n249: type SessionManager interface {\n250:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n251: }\n252: \n253: type APIStatus interface {\n254:     Status() int\n255:     Code() string\n256:     Message() string\n257: }\n258: ```\n259: \n260: ---\n261: \n262: ## API Contracts\n263: \n264: ### Route Table\n265: \n266: | Method | Path | Middleware | Handler |\n267: |--------|------|------------|---------|\n268: | GET | `/health/live` | none | `handleHealthLive` → `{\"status\":\"alive\"}` |\n269: | GET | `/health/ready` | none | `handleHealthReady` → `{\"status\":\"ready\"}` or 503 |\n270: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | concurrency, logging, recovery | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n271: | POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | concurrency, logging, recovery | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n272: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | concurrency, logging, recovery | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n273: | POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | concurrency, logging, recovery | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n274: \n275: ### Request Headers\n276: \n277: | Header | Required | Description |\n278: |--------|----------|-------------|\n279: | `x-agentcube-session-id` | No | Existing session ID for reuse; empty → new session creation |\n280: \n281: ### Response Headers\n282: \n283: | Header | Description |\n284: |--------|-------------|\n285: | `x-agentcube-session-id` | Session ID echoed back for client tracking |\n286: \n287: ### Workload Manager API Calls\n288: \n289: | Endpoint | Method | Request Body | Response |\n290: |----------|--------|--------------|----------|\n291: | `{WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL}/v1/agent-runtime` | POST | `CreateSandboxRequest{kind, name, namespace}` | `CreateSandboxResponse{sessionId, sandboxId, sandboxName, entryPoints}` |\n292: | `{WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL}/v1/code-interpreter` | POST | `CreateSandboxRequest{kind, name, namespace}` | `CreateSandboxResponse{sessionId, sandboxId, sandboxName, entryPoints}` |\n293: \n294: ### JWT Claims Structure\n295: \n296: ```json\n297: {\n298:   \"exp\": <unix timestamp + 5min>,\n299:   \"iat\": <unix timestamp>,\n300:   \"iss\": \"agentcube-router\",\n301:   \"session_id\": \"<session ID>\",\n302:   \"sandbox_id\": \"<sandbox ID>\",\n303:   \"namespace\": \"<sandbox namespace>\",\n304:   \"name\": \"<sandbox name>\"\n305: }\n306: ```\n307: \n308: ---\n309: \n310: ## Error Handling\n311: \n312: ### Custom Error Types (`errors.go`)\n313: \n314: | Error Type | HTTP Status | Code | Message |\n315: |------------|-------------|------|---------|\n316: | `SessionNotFoundError` | 404 | `SESSION_NOT_FOUND` | \"session not found\" |\n317: | `SandboxUnreachableError` | 502 | `SANDBOX_UNREACHABLE` | \"sandbox unreachable\" |\n318: | `SandboxTimeoutError` | 504 | `SANDBOX_TIMEOUT` | \"sandbox timeout\" |\n319: | `JWTSigningError` | 500 | `JWT_SIGNING_FAILED` | \"jwt signing failed\" |\n320: | `ServerOverloadedError` | 429 | `SERVER_OVERLOADED` | \"server overloaded, please try again later\" |\n321: | `NoEntryPointError` | 404 | `NO_ENTRY_POINT` | \"no entry point configured\" |\n322: | `WorkloadManagerError` | Dynamic | `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_ERROR` | Dynamic message |\n323: \n324: ### Error Response Format\n325: \n326: ```json\n327: {\n328:   \"error\": \"<message>\",\n329:   \"code\": \"<error code>\"\n330: }\n331: ```\n332: \n333: ### Error Handling Strategy\n334: \n335: 1. **Session lookup errors**: Return `SessionNotFoundError` when session ID provided but not found in store\n336: 2. **Workload Manager errors**: Wrap HTTP response errors in `WorkloadManagerError` with original status code\n337: 3. **Proxy errors**: Detect \"connection refused\" → 502, \"timeout\" → 504 via string matching\n338: 4. **Entry point errors**: Return 404 if no entry points configured or path prefix not matched\n339: 5. **Concurrency limit**: Return 429 immediately when semaphore full (non-blocking)\n340: \n341: ---\n342: \n343: ## Testing Strategy\n344: \n345: ### Test Coverage Goals\n346: \n347: | Component | Coverage Target | Key Test Cases |\n348: |-----------|-----------------|----------------|\n349: | `session_manager.go` | 90%+ | Existing session lookup, new sandbox creation, WorkloadMgr errors, unsupported kind, empty sessionID in response |\n350: | `server.go` | 85%+ | Route registration, health endpoints, concurrent request limiting, TLS validation, graceful shutdown |\n351: | `jwt.go` | 80%+ | Token generation, claim merging, RSA key creation, PEM encoding/decoding |\n352: | `reverse_proxy.go` | 85%+ | Entry point selection, URL building, proxy director, error handler classification |\n353: | `middleware.go` | 90%+ | Concurrency limit (accept/reject), logging capture, panic recovery |\n354: | `errors.go` | 100% | All error type methods (Error, Status, Code, Message) |\n355: \n356: ### Test Patterns\n357: \n358: 1. **Mock Store**: `MockStore` with function fields for flexible testing\n359: 2. **Mock HTTP Client**: `httptest.Server` for Workload Manager simulation\n360: 3. **Mock SessionManager**: `mockSessionManager` with configurable `getFunc`\n361: 4. **Mock Logger**: `MockLogger` with Info/Error recording for middleware tests\n362: \n363: ### Integration Test Scenarios\n364: \n365: | Scenario | Description |\n366: |----------|-------------|\n367: | Full request flow | Client → Router → mock WorkloadMgr → verify proxy headers |\n368: | Session reuse | Provide existing sessionID → verify no new sandbox created |\n369: | New session creation | Empty sessionID → verify POST to WorkloadMgr, store write |\n370: | TLS startup | EnableTLS=true with missing cert → verify error |\n371: | Graceful shutdown | Context cancellation → verify 10s timeout shutdown |\n372: \n373: ---\n374: \n375: ## Validation Checklist\n376: \n377: - [ ] `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` environment variable required for SessionManager initialization\n378: - [ ] Concurrency limit defaults to 1000 when `MaxConcurrentRequests <= 0`\n379: - [ ] JWT expires in 5 minutes, signed with RS256\n380: - [ ] Session activity updated before and after proxy for accurate idle tracking\n381: - [ ] Entry point selection uses prefix match, falls back to first entry\n382: - [ ] Proxy error classification based on error message content\n383: - [ ] Health check `/health/ready` returns 503 when SessionManager unavailable\n384: - [ ] Gin mode set to ReleaseMode when `config.Debug=false`\n385: \n386: ---\n387: \n388: ## Open Questions\n389: \n390: 1. Should JWT key persistence be mandatory for production deployments (current implementation allows ephemeral keys)?\n391: 2. Should proxy timeout be configurable per entry point (currently hardcoded in transport)?\n392: 3. Should session creation be rate-limited independently from concurrent request limit?\n393: \n394: ---\n395: \n396: ## References\n397: \n398: - `session-routing/design.md` — Session routing module design\n399: - `pkg/router/doc.go` — Interface definitions\n400: - `pkg/common/types/sandbox.go` — SandboxInfo and request/response types\n401: - `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` — Labels, annotations, condition constants\n402: - `deployment/client-go.md` — Kubernetes client library reference\n\n(End of file - total 402 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-010 — Router 会话管理 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-010 — Router 会话管理 |\n| Module | `pkg/router` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\nThe Router module provides HTTP-based session routing for AgentCube sandboxes. It manages session lifecycle, routes incoming invocation requests to appropriate sandbox pods via reverse proxy, and handles JWT-based authentication for secure communication between Router and Workload Manager.\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### System Context\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-010/design.md","time":{"start":1775852464458,"end":1775852464470}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852464475,"sessionID":"ses_286f28ce6ffep8ntWwTGOpmVoB","part":{"id":"prt_d790e2931001SNXvTKgbOgR3Rs","messageID":"msg_d790e08f60015mog30FGLr0pmd","sessionID":"ses_286f28ce6ffep8ntWwTGOpmVoB","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-bb8eee1a1f014abb8d58cd79665e0ae6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，作为 agentcube 的核心数据模型。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: CRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n20: - 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n21: - 类型定义与 DeepCopy 代码分离，由 controller-gen 自动生成\n22: - 支持 status subresource，用于控制器更新资源状态\n23: - Namespaced scope，每个命名空间内独立管理运行时实例\n24: \n25: ### Dependencies\n26: \n27: | Package | Purpose |\n28: |---------|---------|\n29: | `k8s.io/api/core/v1` | PodSpec、EnvVar、PullPolicy、ResourceRequirements 等 |\n30: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` | TypeMeta、ObjectMeta、Condition、Duration |\n31: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema` | GroupVersion、GroupVersionResource |\n32: \n33: ### Controller-gen Markers\n34: \n35: | Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n36: |--------|------------|---------|\n37: | `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | Main type + List type | 注册到 Scheme |\n38: | `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | Main type | 启用 status subresource |\n39: | `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` | Main type | 命名空间级别资源 |\n40: | `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"` | Main type | kubectl 输出列 |\n41: | `+genclient` | Main type | 生成 typed client |\n42: | `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | Main type + List type | DeepCopy 接口 |\n43: \n44: ## Data Structures\n45: \n46: ### groupversion_info.go\n47: \n48: ```go\n49: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n50: package v1alpha1\n51: \n52: import \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n53: \n54: var (\n55:     GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{\n56:         Group:   \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n57:         Version: \"v1alpha1\",\n58:     }\n59:     SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n60:     AddToScheme   = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n61: )\n62: ```\n63: \n64: ### register.go\n65: \n66: ```go\n67: var (\n68:     CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n69:     CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n70:     CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n71:     CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n72: \n73:     AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n74:     AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n75:     AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n76: )\n77: \n78: var SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n79: \n80: func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n81:     return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n82: }\n83: ```\n84: \n85: ### AgentRuntime Types\n86: \n87: ```go\n88: // +genclient\n89: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n90: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n91: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n92: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n93: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n94: type AgentRuntime struct {\n95:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n96:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n97:     Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n98:     Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n99: }\n100: \n101: type AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n102:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n103:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n104:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n105:     Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,opt,name=podTemplate\"`\n106:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n107:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n108:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,opt,name=sessionTimeout\"`\n109:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n110:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n111:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=maxSessionDuration\"`\n112: }\n113: \n114: type AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n115:     // +optional\n116:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n117: }\n118: \n119: type SandboxTemplate struct {\n120:     // +optional\n121:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,rep,name=labels\"`\n122:     // +optional\n123:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,rep,name=annotations\"`\n124:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n125:     Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=spec\"`\n126: }\n127: \n128: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n129: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n130: type AgentRuntimeList struct {\n131:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n132:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n133:     Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n134: }\n135: ```\n136: \n137: ### CodeInterpreter Types\n138: \n139: ```go\n140: // +genclient\n141: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n142: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n143: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n144: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n145: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n146: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n147:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n148:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n149:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n150:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n151: }\n152: \n153: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n154:     // +optional\n155:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n156:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n157:     Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n158:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n159:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n160:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n161:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n162:     // +optional\n163:     WarmPoolSize *int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n164:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n165:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n166:     // +optional\n167:     AuthMode AuthModeType `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n168: }\n169: \n170: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n171:     // +optional\n172:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n173:     // +optional\n174:     Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n175: }\n176: \n177: type CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n178:     // +optional\n179:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n180:     // +optional\n181:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n182:     // +optional\n183:     RuntimeClassName *string `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n184:     Image string `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n185:     // +optional\n186:     ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n187:     // +optional\n188:     // +patchMergeKey=name\n189:     // +patchStrategy=merge\n190:     // +listType=map\n191:     // +listMapKey=name\n192:     ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n193:     // +optional\n194:     Environment []corev1.EnvVar `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n195:     // +optional\n196:     // +listType=atomic\n197:     Command []string `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n198:     // +optional\n199:     Args []string `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n200:     // +optional\n201:     Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n202: }\n203: \n204: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n205: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n206: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n207:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n208:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n209:     Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n210: }\n211: ```\n212: \n213: ### Shared Types\n214: \n215: ```go\n216: type TargetPort struct {\n217:     // +optional\n218:     PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n219:     // +optional\n220:     Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n221:     Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n222:     // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n223:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS;\n224:     Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n225: }\n226: \n227: type AuthModeType string\n228: \n229: const (\n230:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n231:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n232: )\n233: \n234: type ProtocolType string\n235: \n236: const (\n237:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n238:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n239: )\n240: ```\n241: \n242: ## API Schema\n243: \n244: ### CRD OpenAPI Constraints\n245: \n246: | Resource | Required Spec Fields |\n247: |----------|----------------------|\n248: | AgentRuntime | `targetPort`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration` |\n249: | CodeInterpreter | `template` |\n250: \n251: ### Defaults\n252: \n253: | Field | Default Value |\n254: |-------|---------------|\n255: | `sessionTimeout` | `15m` |\n256: | `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` |\n257: | `authMode` | `picod` |\n258: | `targetPort[].protocol` | `HTTP` |\n259: \n260: ### Enums\n261: \n262: | Field | Allowed Values |\n263: |-------|----------------|\n264: | `authMode` | `picod`, `none` |\n265: | `protocol` | `HTTP`, `HTTPS` |\n266: \n267: ### REST Resource Plurals\n268: \n269: | Kind | Plural |\n270: |------|--------|\n271: | AgentRuntime | `agentruntimes` |\n272: | CodeInterpreter | `codeinterpreters` |\n273: \n274: ### Printer Columns\n275: \n276: | Name | Type | JSONPath |\n277: |------|------|----------|\n278: | Age | date | `.metadata.creationTimestamp` |\n279: \n280: ## Error Handling\n281: \n282: - 无 spec 必填字段时，API server 拒绝创建请求（validation error）\n283: - 无效 enum 值时，API server 返回 validation error\n284: - Duration 格式错误时，使用 Go `metav1.Duration` 解析失败抛出错误\n285: \n286: ## Testing Strategy\n287: \n288: ### Unit Tests\n289: \n290: | Test Category | Coverage |\n291: |---------------|----------|\n292: | DeepCopy generation | 确保 DeepCopy 方法正确复制所有字段（deep vs shallow） |\n293: | Default values | 验证 kubebuilder 默认值标记生效 |\n294: | Enum validation | 测试所有允许值及无效值 |\n295: | JSON serialization | 验证 JSON tag 正确映射 |\n296: \n297: ### Integration Tests\n298: \n299: - CRD 安装验证：确保 `make gen-crd` 生成的 YAML 可被 k8s API server 接受\n300: - Client-go 生成验证：`make gen-client` 生成的 client/informer/lister 可正常使用\n301: \n302: ### Test File Structure\n303: \n304: ```\n305: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n306:   types_test.go       — DeepCopy、默认值、JSON 序列化测试\n307: ```\n308: \n309: ### Test Utilities\n310: \n311: 使用 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/webhook` 进行 validation 测试（如需 webhook）。\n312: \n313: ## File Structure\n314: \n315: ```\n316: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n317:   groupversion_info.go   — GroupVersion 定义、SchemeBuilder\n318:   register.go            — Kind constants、Resource helper\n319:   agentruntime_types.go  — AgentRuntime、AgentRuntimeList、SandboxTemplate\n320:   codeinterpreter_types.go — CodeInterpreter、CodeInterpreterList、共享类型\n321:   doc.go                 — 包文档（可选）\n322: \n323: client-go/                — 由 make gen-client 生成\n324:   clientset/\n325:   informers/\n326:   listers/\n327: ```\n328: \n329: ## Generation Commands\n330: \n331: | Command | Output |\n332: |---------|--------|\n333: | `make generate` | DeepCopy 代码 + CRD YAML（`manifests/charts/base/crds/`） |\n334: | `make gen-client` | client-go（clientset、informers、listers） |\n335: | `make gen-all` | 以上全部 |\n336: \n337: ## Open Questions\n338: \n339: - [已解决] 默认值由 kubebuilder markers 定义\n340: - [已解决] Status 字段包含 `Conditions`（通用）和 `Ready`（CodeInterpreter）\n341: - 是否需要添加 additionalPrinterColumns（如 Ready 状态）？\n342: - 是否需要 webhook 进行更复杂验证？\n343: \n344: ## References\n345: \n346: - Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n347: - client-go: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n348: - controller-tools version: `v0.17.2`\n\n(End of file - total 348 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，作为 agentcube 的核心数据模型。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\nCRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n- 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","time":{"start":1775852464460,"end":1775852464473}}}}
