{"type":"text","timestamp":1775852630827,"sessionID":"ses_286f28ce6ffep8ntWwTGOpmVoB","part":{"id":"prt_d7910a718001CENRq7pEoCEerp","messageID":"msg_d79108666001R50ronGyQjpE5E","sessionID":"ses_286f28ce6ffep8ntWwTGOpmVoB","type":"text","text":"Written comprehensive design.md for AR-011 at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/design.md` (594 lines). Covers architecture, JWTManager data structures, token generation/verification flows, key management with Kubernetes Secrets, error handling, testing strategy, and implementation checklist aligned with existing `pkg/router/jwt.go` implementation.","time":{"start":1775852630825,"end":1775852630825}}}
